testcase.name: Given complex nested structure Return properly flattened form urlencoded string()
Given object with nested objects Return flattened form urlencoded string()
Given object with special characters Return properly encoded string()
Given simple object with primitive values Return valid form urlencoded string()
Given object with array values Return valid form urlencoded string with repeated keys()
Given array as root Return indexed key-value pairs()
Given empty object Return empty string()
